Mr.Dhurat, 1st Asstt. to Court Receiver present. P.C. : P.C. : P.C. : By the present Judge s Order, the Plaintiffs are seeking to dispose of the goods by private treatee. I have perused the valuation report dated 27.4.1991 filed by K.H.Parkar who has opined that the goods are not worth even valuation. 2. In view thereof, I have signed the Judge s Order and place it on record. Judge s Order disposed of accordingly.
